搭建自己的VPN服务器，享受科学上网的快感。全平台包括Mac、Linux、Windows、Android、iOS均可使用。费用低至3.99美元每年（仅为市面上主流的翻墙软件价格的十分之一）。<!--more-->

<strong>适用场景</strong>

上Google、Facebook、Twitter等。看Youtube视频可能会有卡顿，不过升级服务器配置应该就能解决。

<strong>原料</strong>
<ul>
	<li>Paypal账户</li>
	<li>Shadowsocksx软件</li>
	<li>浏览器</li>
</ul>
<strong>步骤</strong>
<ol>
	<li>选主机配置：到<a href="http://bandwagonhost.leisudeng.com/cheapvps">搬瓦工</a>网站选择适合你的主机配置。最低3.99刀每年，也是笔者亲测的套餐。点击"去购买"。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.32.07-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-264" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.32.07-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.32.07 PM" width="1994" height="1082" /></a></li>
	<li>点击Add to Cart，确定主机配置<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.34.16-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-265" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.34.16-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.34.16 PM" width="1424" height="1058" /></a></li>
	<li>点击Checkout，确定订单。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.35.07-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-266" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.35.07-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.35.07 PM" width="2004" height="842" /></a></li>
	<li>填写基本信息，注册账号，用Paypal支付。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.36.05-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-267" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.36.05-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.36.05 PM" width="1780" height="1456" /></a></li>
	<li>支付完后，跳转回搬瓦工主站，选择My Services。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.36.56-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-268" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.36.56-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.36.56 PM" width="2072" height="936" /></a></li>
	<li>稍等片刻，等到Status变为Active后，点击KiwiVM Control Panel。</li>
	<li><a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.37.16-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-269" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.37.16-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.37.16 PM" width="1956" height="334" /></a>选择下方Install Shadowsockx<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.38.07-PM.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-270" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.38.07-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.38.07 PM" width="300" height="814" /></a></li>
	<li>配置加密类型、端口号与密码。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.38.22-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-271" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.38.22-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.38.22 PM" width="1332" height="580" /></a></li>
	<li>至此，服务器端已经OK了。接下来配置本机。下面以Mac平台做演示。</li>
	<li>安装Shadowsockx（可通过brew install来安装），打开配置选项。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.39.00-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-272" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.39.00-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.39.00 PM" width="1102" height="728" /></a></li>
	<li>填写服务器信息，包括IP地址、端口号、加密类型和密码。<a href="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.39.23-PM.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-273" src="http://shuailong.me/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-14-at-8.39.23-PM.png" alt="Screen Shot 2015-03-14 at 8.39.23 PM" width="1034" height="654" /></a></li>
